We also\ncrucially use very deep Y. Yomdin's entropy estimates of near critical values\nfor polynomials (based on algebraic geometry tools).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Sep 2018 01:57:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 Sep 2018 08:40:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-20"}
