tiple real-image viewpoint estimation datasets, such as\nPascal3D+ and ObjectNet3D. To encourage reproducible research, we have released\nthe codes for our proposed approach.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Sep 2018 11:16:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-05"}
