 be\nexpected, and in the meantime, the accompanying electromagnetic radiations from\nhadronic processes will not cause any enhancement in the blazar's\nelectromagnetic flux.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Sep 2018 13:54:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Dec 2022 03:50:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-29"}
